                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The documents printed and cited in this section are considerably illuminated by
                    contemporary diary notes and other materials written by a number of the ranking
                    participants in the discussions of this subject within the United States
                    Government. See particularly Hull, pp. 1602 ff.; Stimson and Bundy, pp. 568 ff.;
                    and Morgenthau materials printed in Blum, pp. 339 ff., and <hi rend="italic"
                        >Morgenthau Diary</hi> (<hi rend="italic">Germany</hi>), vol. I, pp. 415 ff.
                    See also <ref target="frus1944v01#pg_276">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1944, vol. I, pp. 276</ref>
                    ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
